  2→ * Milestone 4: HTTP Endpoints and Governance Feed
  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-AL-004 (learning governance feed cards), US-AL-001 (human creates learning)
  5→ *
  6→ * Validates:
  7→ * - POST create learning with embedding generation
  8→ * - GET list with filters (status, type, agent)
  9→ * - Approve action transitions pending to active with audit trail
 10→ * - Edit & Approve modifies text and activates
 11→ * - Dismiss action records reason
 12→ * - Deactivate action with audit trail
 13→ * - Pending learnings appear in governance feed
 14→ *
 15→ * Driving ports:
 16→ *   POST   /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings                     (create learning)
 17→ *   GET    /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings                     (list learnings)
