  1→/**
  2→ * Milestone 3: Full Learning Lifecycle
  3→ *
  4→ * Traces: US-LL-03 (edit/deactivate), US-LL-04 (create with targeting)
  5→ *
  6→ * End-to-end lifecycle tests that combine creation with agent targeting,
  7→ * editing, and deactivation into complete user journeys.
  8→ *
  9→ * What is NOT tested here (already covered elsewhere):
 10→ *   - Basic create/approve/dismiss (agent-learnings/milestone-4)
 11→ *   - Basic deactivate (agent-learnings/milestone-4)
 12→ *   - Single filter operations (agent-learnings/milestone-4)
 13→ *
 14→ * What IS tested here:
 15→ *   - Create with specific target_agents -> verify agent filter visibility
 16→ *   - Create with empty target_agents -> verify universal visibility
 17→ *   - Full lifecycle: create -> edit -> deactivate -> verify invisible
 18→ *   - Deactivated learnings no longer appear in agent-filtered views
 19→ *   - Multiple learnings lifecycle in same workspace
 20→ *
 21→ * Driving ports:
 22→ *   POST   /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings                     (create)
 23→ *   PUT    /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings/:learningId         (edit -- NEW)
 24→ *   POST   /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings/:learningId/actions (deactivate)
 25→ *   GET    /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/learnings                     (list + verify)
